{"tid":2261814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聽障男學生被指搶胡椒噴霧使高級警司跌倒　高級警司區永樑：雙膝「爛咗」、右膝滲血","createTime":"2020-10-28T15:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T16:51:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"66831e485a9b87db1f390abdbb41fd272eaa409a","tid":2261814,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"去年 9 月 15 日港島區遊行期間，一名聽障男學生被指企圖搶去警司胡椒噴霧，期間令對方擦傷。男學生否認一項襲警罪，今（28 日）在東區裁判法院受審，期間需戴上耳機。聲稱受襲的時仼高級警司區永樑供稱，案發時被告雙手捉住其胡椒噴劑，大力拉扯，他因而失平衡倒地，雙方在地上繼續糾纏，期間他的右側肩膀、頸及右邊耳後位置被踢，事後雙膝「爛咗」、後腦有痛楚、右耳後流血及右邊鎖骨位紅腫。<br />\n<br />\n案發時仼高級警司的區永樑現升職為總警司，他供稱，案發當日為東九龍應變大隊副指揮官，身穿軍裝執勤。下午 5 時，他收到指示有不少非法集結人士在港島區破壞及設路障，遂與大隊從港鐵金鐘站，乘坐特別列車到銅鑼灣掃蕩。在銅鑼灣掃蕩至近晚上 6 時 45 分，他收到指示要返回港鐵銅鑼灣站，大隊一行約 430 人，便一直行至銅鑼灣站 C 出口。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">區永樑續指，為防情況惡化，他拿出胡椒噴劑，警告人群離開。被告卻雙手捉住胡椒噴劑、用力拉扯，「感覺想搶走枝噴劑」，被告並大叫，「好似一個人發力時的叫聲，好似一個人打網球時『啊！』的聲音。」</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%81%BD%E9%9A%9C%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%90%B6%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E5%99%B4%E9%9C%A7%E4%BD%BF%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8%E8%B7%8C%E5%80%92-%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8-%E9%9B%99%E8%86%9D-%E7%88%9B%E5%92%97-%E5%8F%B3%E8%86%9D%E6%BB%B2%E8%A1%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%2581%25BD%25E9%259A%259C%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2590%25B6%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E5%2599%25B4%25E9%259C%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25B7%258C%25E5%2580%2592-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25B8-%25E9%259B%2599%25E8%2586%259D-%25E7%2588%259B%25E5%2592%2597-%25E5%258F%25B3%25E8%2586%259D%25E6%25BB%25B2%25E8%25A1%2580%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7Dv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=192afe23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%2581%25BD%25E9%259A%259C%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2590%25B6%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E5%2599%25B4%25E9%259C%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25B7%258C%25E5%2580%2592-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25B8-%25E9%259B%2599%25E8%2586%259D-%25E7%2588%259B%25E5%2592%2597-%25E5%258F%25B3%25E8%2586%259D%25E6%25BB%25B2%25E8%25A1%2580%2F&h=be7a8f47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%81%BD%E9%9A%9C%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%90%B6%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E5%99%B4%E9%9C%A7%E4%BD%BF%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8%E8%B7%8C%E5%80%92-%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8-%E9%9B%99%E8%86%9D-%E7%88%9B%E5%92%97-%E5%8F%B3%E8%86%9D%E6%BB%B2%E8%A1%80/</a>"},{"pid":"2ef5ce0359159ebe5a0932d80e11557579c1f101","tid":2261814,"uid":211110,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:07:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb69b2d12b749c22095a510f0199e37b92dc227f","tid":2261814,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">此案由鄭紀航審理</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c3ff2a3106b6ebed0c58ecb8ecd5fa3c09553d5d","tid":2261814,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:09:09.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"1f5ac42e952ec0ad1a4e325143c2d36f00eea8d2","tid":2261814,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27eb2c1ffeda761aefc214742bee39976900534c","tid":2261814,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb69b2d12b749c22095a510f0199e37b92dc2